    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents the pinnacle of its model year. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless paint and pristine leather interior to the engine bay, which looks as though it just rolled off the assembly line. It has been garage-kept, regularly detailed, and serviced strictly according to manufacturer schedules. Buyers can expect a car that drives like new with no mechanical issues, aesthetic blemishes, or wear. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast seeking the absolute best example available on the market.",
