    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-loved ride? This vehicle is in great shape and ready for its next adventure! It has been consistently maintained and delivers a smooth, dependable driving experience that you can count on. While it shows a few signs of careful use, it remains a fantastic choice for anyone seeking a quality car that's been treated with respect. Come see why this solid performer is the perfect addition to your driveway!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
